{"tid":1073523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 做錯事犯法好內疚想去警署自守，但屋企人唔俾","createTime":"2019-03-22T17:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:31:40.000Z","uid":97606,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a64fa7921b7f68564ad2eff22d0c8923123887e3","tid":1073523,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"我知道自己罪孽深重<br />\n我打呢篇文上嚟亦都唔係為咗搏同情<br />\n如果有人睇完想報警嘅話我亦都唔會怨佢<br />\n因為我已經食唔安瞓唔落成個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n件事係咁的<br />\n上個禮拜我同班同學VA堂做緊group勞作<br />\n其實份勞作就好簡單嘅，剪剪貼貼就ok<br />\n點知落完堂放學行行下翻屋企<br />\n見到後面個師奶同個女唔知喺到笑啲乜<br />\n一摸個背脊先知原來俾人貼咗張細細哋嘅memo紙<br />\n上面畫咗隻龜<br />\n當時我眼火爆，無諗咁多直接掉咗張紙落地就算<br />\n但之後返到屋企越諗越唔對路<br />\n我唔單止亂拋垃圾，而且仲要有目擊證人望到，水洗都唔清，張紙上面仲要有我指紋<br />\n之後嗰晚我成晚都瞓唔著，個腦係咁諗住自己會唔會俾人告，甚至要去坐監<br />\n第二日我同爸爸媽媽講我想去自守，因為聽人講個罪名會輕啲<br />\n我明白紙包唔住火，終有一日啲警察會查到上門<br />\n到時我嘅情況只會比而加更差<br />\n但佢哋無體諒我不突止，仲問我係咪傻咗<br />\n叫我唔好再提呢件事，當無發生過就算<br />\n但我始終都係過唔到自己嗰關，直到今日我放咗學<br />\n去咗佢哋面前話食埋晚飯就會去報警自守<br />\n佢哋嚇到傻晒咁沒收咗我電話，叫我入房打機<br />\nweekend唔準出門好好地喺屋企休息下就會無事<br />\n我而加一路喊住一路打緊呢篇文上嚟<br />\n希望呢到有人可以話我聽之後應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e45b476cffa8f47daa3c3afc1a64e131ceb757f","tid":1073523,"uid":15,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"見無人覆你咁慘, 我覆下你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LwTAt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LwTAt.gif&h=31f9de48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f040986d606ee3951fd8c5b08b1f56b44ddf75b","tid":1073523,"uid":201414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"冇點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主係假膠撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9123905e33e7158271ce0f27019759f2b1b70e","tid":1073523,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e80bffc96a83ca95987dff21b8234c55e6e1497","tid":1073523,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f040986d606ee3951fd8c5b08b1f56b44ddf75b","tid":1073523,"uid":201414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"冇點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主係假膠撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5301d8c5e1bf293f8d443a155b9257195f7d9779","tid":1073523,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"下次返去癡晒所有人嘅背隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話比人知你唔係好蝦<br />\n將你失去嘅尊嚴一次過攞晒返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb75f113b11e96e931b3bfd2dffcf38aa610dd3","tid":1073523,"uid":207844,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"087f7493706f8c412815493fd2d590832f5914e9","tid":1073523,"uid":76697,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:19:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b25cad9e7b0106bcf745641dbe91d786353cc175","tid":1073523,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:24:22.000Z","msg":"自首啦，應該會幫你轉介青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8326bce6a7e0fe1a5aad38537b8fe3677bfd4c87","tid":1073523,"uid":206895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T20:19:30.000Z","msg":"警已報<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQKtyuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQKtyuk.jpg&h=43fd5674&s={SIZE}\" />